OL,3,CTeens in custody after causing fire
OL,4,Cand #15m damage at Grade-listed hall
OL,6,FTwo teenage boys have been sent to
OL,7,Fcustody after torching a Grade II-
OL,8,Flisted building in Newcastle and
OL,9,Fcausing #15m worth of damage.
OL,11,FThe 17-year-olds set a shower curtain
OL,12,Falight inside the Newcastle University
OL,13,Fowned Henderson Hall in Heaton,
OL,14,Fcausing a fire which spread across the
OL,15,Fproperty.
OL,17,FWatch the footage of the Grade II
OL,18,Flisted building on fire from June last
OL,19,Fyear
