OL,6,FThe Youth Court on North Tyneside
OL,7,Fheard how the boys bragged, boasted
OL,8,Fand recorded the incident on their
OL,9,Fmobile phones and posted on Snapchat.
OL,10,FThey also posed for a picture together
OL,11,Fwhile each smoking a cigarette.
OL,13,FGurjot Kaur, prosecuting, told the
OL,14,Fcourt how they had been in contact on
OL,15,FSnapchat and one of them had asked the
OL,16,Fother if he wanted to go to an
OL,17,Fabandoned building in Heaton.
