OL,6,FShe said they gained entry to the
OL,7,Fformer student accommodation, which
OL,8,Fhad been derelict for years, through a
OL,9,Fdamaged window on 8 June last year.
OL,11,FVideo footage, which they captured at
OL,12,Fthe scene, showed one of the youths
OL,13,Ftrying to set fire to a mattress and
OL,14,Fthe other blowing it out.
OL,16,FIn another video, the same defendant
OL,17,Fcould be seen using a purple lighter
OL,18,Fto set fire to the shower curtain.
