OL,6,FWhen they realise the flames had
OL,7,Fturned into a bigger blaze, the same
OL,8,Fdefendant decided to record a video
OL,9,Ffor Snapchat in which he could be
OL,10,Fheard saying they were going to "burn
OL,11,Fthe building down".
OL,13,FThe court heard the other youth then
OL,14,Fbragged about the fire.
OL,16,FMiss Kaur said a member of university
OL,17,Fstaff, who is based at the campus, saw
OL,18,Fa large cloud of smoke as he was
OL,19,Fwalking along. He spotted two males on
OL,20,Fthe roof and shouted at them saying:
OL,21,F"Get off, it's not worth your life."
