OL,6,FOne teenager managed to escape over a
OL,7,Ffence however the worker stopped the
OL,8,Fother male from doing the same. Miss
OL,9,FKaur said he was able to grab his
OL,10,Fbackpack and detain him on the ground.
OL,12,FThe youth, who managed to escape, went
OL,13,Fon to send voice notes to another
OL,14,Fperson in which he said he needed to
OL,15,Favoid the police.
OL,17,FMiss Kaur told the court in North
OL,18,FShields how 14 calls had been made to
OL,19,F999 about the fire at Henderson Hall.
