OL,6,FShe said the cost of the damage was
OL,7,F#15m and this did not include the
OL,8,Fadditional cost of insurance cover.
OL,9,FShe said the cover was now #400,000
OL,10,Fdue to the premium doubling.
OL,12,FBoth males, who cannot be named for
OL,13,Flegal reasons, admitted carrying out
OL,14,Farson at Henderson Hall and destroying
OL,15,F#15m worth of property during a
OL,16,Fprevious hearing last month.
OL,18,FThey were sentenced during separate
OL,19,Fhearings at the Youth Court on
OL,20,FWednesday.
