OL,6,F"A fire he could film for whatever
OL,7,Fpurpose - Snapchat I don't know - but
OL,8,Fit would burn out with the tiles in
OL,9,Fthe confines of that area. That seems
OL,10,Fto be the thinking that was going
OL,11,Fthrough his mind at that time."
OL,13,FHe said that the teenager now
OL,14,Frecognises that any fire could result
OL,15,Fin what happened on that day.
