OL,6,FThe defendant, who was dressed in a
OL,7,Fblack shirt and blue jeans, said: "I
OL,8,Fthink it's quite obvious the thought
OL,9,Fprocess about sending me away. You see
OL,10,Fthe videos and you see the figure and
OL,11,F15 mil, but at the end of the day it
OL,12,Fwas unintentional, it was reckless, it
OL,13,Fwas stupid."
OL,15,FHe told them he had been "quite
OL,16,Ftraumatised" by the thought that if
OL,17,Fthings had gone differently that day
OL,18,Fhe might not be standing there. He
OL,19,Fsaid that he has also avoided
OL,20,Freoffending while on bail.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/15
