OL,6,FMr Fleet asked him: "Once you realised
OL,7,Fthe fire was getting out of control
OL,8,Fwhy did neither of you think to phone
OL,9,Fthe fire brigade?"
OL,11,FHe replied: "I don't know, I think we
OL,12,Fwere too focused on getting out of the
OL,13,Fbuilding because it was stupidly fast.
OL,14,FWe couldn't see in front of us. It was
OL,15,Fone of the scariest times of my life.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/15
