OL,4,Cand #15m damage at Grade-listed hall
OL,6,FThe teenager, who was dressed in a
OL,7,Fblue suit, shirt and tie, was handed a
OL,8,Ffour month detention and training
OL,9,Forder. Ms Lamb told the court that she
OL,10,Fwould be appealing the sentence handed
OL,11,Fto him.
OL,13,FAt the height of the blaze, thick
OL,14,Fblack smoke could be seen billowing
OL,15,Finto the sky for miles around Tyneside.
OL,17,FThere were 10 appliances on scene
OL,18,Falong with two aerial ladder
OL,19,Fplatforms, and crews remained
OL,20,Fthroughout the night to keep the fire
OL,21,Funder control.
